title: Blackout Comedy Vol.4
desc: Blackout Comedy Vol. 4. Live free comedy featuring some of NYC's funniest comedians. This months headliner Rob Cantrell (Last Comic Standing, Tough Crowd) featuring Marie Faustin, Julie Kottakis and Mick DiFlo. Hosted by Drew Dowdy and Sean O'Hagan with Iron Nigel spinning on the 1's and 2's. Drink Specials and happy hour all show at Jeromes 155 Rivington, LES, come out and support. Show time 8pm.
